text.tspan: Under the inner cone is logic and power cables
There will also voltage converters and logic controllers in boxes under the cone
Inner cone supports LEDs wraped around it
On top of the LEDs is foam
Foam is covered with light fabric that can be removed with a zipper on the bottom
Fabric not over LEDs will be standard firsuit fabric (Still removable overall)
Platform to put LEDs and foam 1 1/8"
